  <p>最寄駅<br><input class="text" type="text" name="station"></p><br>
  <p>甘さ<br>控えめ<input class="range" type="range" min="1" max="5" step="1" name="sweet">甘い</p><br>
  <p>氷のタイプ<br>サラサラ<input class="range" type="range" min="1" max="5" step="1" name="ice">フワフワ</p><br>
  <p>ボリューム<br>軽い<input class="range" type="range" min="1" max="5" step="1" name="size">重い</p><br>
  <p>本格度<br>簡易的<input class="range" type="range" min="1" max="5" step="1" name="plo">本格的</p><br>
  <p>値段<br>500円<input class="range" type="range" min="1" max="5" step="1" name="price">2000円</p><br>

  <input class="submit" type="submit" value="POST">
</form>
</div>
